sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Tech Data Corp. (Symbol: TECD), where a total of 3,742 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 374,200 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 94.4% of TECD's average daily trading volume over the past month of 396,530 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $100 strike call option expiring December 15, 2017 , with 759 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 75,900 underlying shares of TECD.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) saw options trading volume of 39,682 contracts, representing approximately 4.0 million underlying shares or approximately 89.1% of HD's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 4.5 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $170 strike call option expiring December 15, 2017 , with 2,374 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 237,400 underlying shares of HD.

Especially high volume was seen for the $48 strike call option expiring December 15, 2017 , with 17,178 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 1.7 million underlying shares of MU.
